        </item>
        <item>
            <title>1.3.0</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:07:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/martinfekete10/Tuneful/releases</link>
            <sparkle:version>1.3.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.3.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>New mini player options and volume adjustments</h1>
<ul>
<li>New feature to customize the look of mini player - you can now choose from 2 styles</li>
<li>You can now hide mini player window by right-clicking and choosing Hide window option</li>
<li>Mini player is now easier to move around</li>
<li>Volume slider now adjusts Apple Music/Spotify instead of a system volume</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
