        <item>
            <title>1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:44:35 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/martinfekete10/Tuneful/releases</link>
            <sparkle:version>1.2.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[<h1>More customisation and Apple Music favorites fix</h1>
<ul>
<li>You can now choose if you want to have a transparent background or blurred artwork of current song as a background, both in menu bar popover and mini player window</li>
<li>Fixed a bug where songs were not being added to Apple Music favorites after clicking heart button</li>
<li>Changed Add to Favorites icon from heart to star to make it consistent with Apple Music</li>
</ul>]]></description>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
